trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerInfoCollection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `transformers` section of the `webParts` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: A classe TransformerInfoCollection permite acessar e modificar programaticamente o `transformers` seção o `webParts` seção de um arquivo de configuração.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> objects, as part of a TransformerInfoCollection, specify custom classes that extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>objetos, como parte de um TransformerInfoCollection, especificam classes personalizadas que estendem a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer></xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>

trans-unit.source: These transformer classes act as bridges between connected Web Parts, translating data sent by a connection provider into something that the connection consumer can accept.
trans-unit.target: Essas classes de transformador atuam como pontes entre Web Parts conectadas, conversão de dados enviados por um provedor de conexão em algo que o consumidor de conexão pode aceitar.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerInfoCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: O construtor TransformerInfoCollection não se destina a ser usado diretamente no seu código.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: Ele é chamado pelo sistema de configuração do ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A>propriedade o <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection>classe sempre contém uma instância do <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection>tipo.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use this instance, rather than creating your own.
trans-unit.target: Use esta instância, em vez de criar seus próprios.
